_________________________Q2__________________________________________

Create a trigger to handle inserts to the product relation ( if price < 50 the set
price to 90)


mysql> SELECT * FROM product;
+-----+--------+-------+
| pid | pname  | price |
+-----+--------+-------+
|  11 | MANGO  |   112 |
|  12 | mat    |    20 |
|  13 | tomato |    41 |
|  14 | apple  |    41 |
|  15 | FAN    |   200 |
+-----+--------+-------+
5 rows in set (0.00 sec)

mysql> delimiter //
mysql> create trigger prodt_price
    -> before insert
    -> on product
    -> for each row 
    -> begin
    -> if new.price < 50 then
    -> set new.price=90;
    -> end if;
    -> end//
Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.06 sec)


mysql> delimiter ;
mysql> insert into product values(16,'phone',40);
Query OK, 1 row affected (0.04 sec)

mysql> select* from product;
+-----+--------+-------+
| pid | pname  | price |
+-----+--------+-------+
|  11 | MANGO  |   112 |
|  12 | mat    |    20 |
|  13 | tomato |    41 |
|  14 | apple  |    41 |
|  15 | FAN    |   200 |
|  16 | phone  |    90 |
+-----+--------+-------+
6 rows in set (0.00 sec)

